">李沐宸,刘旭威,陈柏融,游乐儿,译泽,张皓承</p></div></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><div class=" gifpic" style="background: url(https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://pic1.iqiyipic.com/lequ/common/lego/20251220/bc0619b1dc7d425092def0d76bec0f9c.jpg) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;padding-top: 30%;border-radius: 5px;position: relative;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">开播吧短剧季2025</p><p class="info">更新至20251221期</p></div></div><a class="dymrslide banner jpgpic" data-name="开播吧短剧季2025" data-fname="更新至20251221期" href="/index.php/vod/play/id/135670/sid/1/nid/1.html" style="background: url(https://images.weserv.nl/?url=https://pic1.iqiyipic.com/lequ/common/lego/20251220/bc0619b1dc7d425092def0d76bec0f9c.jpg) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">开播吧短剧季2025</p><p class="info">李语家</p></div></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><div class=" gifpic" style="background: url(https://vcover-hz-pic.puui.qpic.cn/vcover_hz_pic/0/mzc00200li7mfpr1729225233223/0) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;padding-top: 30%;border-radius: 5px;position: relative;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">脱口秀和Ta的朋友们第二季</p><p class="info">更新至20250905(脱口秀精编)</p></div></div><a class="dymrslide banner jpgpic" data-name="脱口秀和Ta的朋友们第二季" data-fname="更新至20250905(脱口秀精编)" href="/index.php/vod/play/id/119240/sid/1/nid/1.html" style="background: url(https://tv.puui.qpic.cn/tv/0/mz_tv_image_frontend_442f1e-8_1866655150_1751946530761423_pic_1920x800/0?imageView2/2/w/1680) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">脱口秀和Ta的朋友们第二季</p><p class="info">更新至20250905(脱口秀精编)</p></div></a></div><div class="swiper-slide"><div class=" gifpic" style="background: url(https://1vimg.hitv.com/100/2507/0818/3501/25VSUgX9aw/444205741667897344.jpg) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;padding-top: 30%;border-radius: 5px;position: relative;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">密室大逃脱第七季</p><p class="info">收官宴</p></div></div><a class="dymrslide banner jpgpic" data-name="密室大逃脱第七季" data-fname="收官宴" href="/index.php/vod/play/id/121339/sid/1/nid/1.html" style="background: url(https://1vimg.hitv.com/100/2507/0818/3501/25VSUgX9aw/444205741667897344.jpg) center no-repeat; background-size: cover;"><div class="focus_leftshode focusleftshode"></div><div class="focus_rightshode focusrightshode"></div><div class="focus_topshode focustopshode"></div><div class="focus_bottomshode focusbottomshode"></div><div class="txt-info"><p class="gate"><span>综艺</span></p><p class="name">密室大逃脱第七季</p><p class="info">大张伟,彭昱畅,杨幂,许凯,周笔畅,张宥浩</p></div></a></div></div><div class="swiper-pagination"></div></div><main id="index-main" class="wrapper"><div class="content"><br><div class="module"><div class="module-heading"><h2 class="module-title">最新热播</h2><div class="module-sub-title"></div></div><div class="module-list module-lines-list"><div class="module-items"><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/907/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="吞噬星空" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.jisuimage.com/cover/1e81d9ddb81fa08481c942a7f794300e.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="吞噬星空"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2020</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-ru"><span class="rebo">热播</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/907/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="吞噬星空">吞噬星空</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B5%B5%E4%B9%BE%E6%99%AF.html" target="_blank">赵乾景</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B0%A2%E8%8E%B9.html" target="_blank">谢莹</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AE%8B%E5%9B%BD%E5%BA%86.html" target="_blank">宋国庆</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%BB%84%E8%BF%9B%E5%88%99.html" target="_blank">黄进则</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%BC%A0%E8%8B%A5%E7%91%9C.html" target="_blank">张若瑜</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　某一天，地球上出现了不明来由的RR病毒，将世界卷入灾难之中。受到感染的动物变异成为可怕的怪兽，大举入侵，人类面临毁灭之际筑起了围墙，成立基地市作为人类最后的堡垒。人类在这一段时间经历的磨难，被称为</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/907/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="吞噬星空">吞噬星空</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至230集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/179154/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="莫离2026" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/b97da3de4557055c12fdc708c08d179d.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="莫离2026"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">连续剧</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-ru"><span class="rebo">热播</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/179154/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="莫离2026">莫离2026</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%99%BD%E9%B9%BF.html" target="_blank">白鹿</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%9E%E7%A3%8A.html" target="_blank">丞磊</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%94%A1%E6%AD%A3%E6%9D%B0.html" target="_blank">蔡正杰</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%A8%E8%88%92%E4%BC%8A.html" target="_blank">杨舒伊</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">叶府的长女叶璃（白鹿 饰），嫁去破败的定王府，和双腿残疾的定王墨修尧成亲，而在叶璃出嫁当日，黎王墨景黎与叶府次女叶莹也于同日成亲。叶璃作为离山后人，曾被封在山中八年，婚后她表面无事，实则暗中谋划，将当</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/179154/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="莫离2026">莫离2026</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第40集已完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1066/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="仙逆" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.jisuimage.com/cover/896b690b9566f53a875e03a3a324c091.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="仙逆"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2023</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>中国大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-ru"><span class="rebo">热播</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1066/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="仙逆">仙逆</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　乡村平凡少年王林，为了心中不屈的信念踏入仙门修行，克服天资不足的困境，逆流而上，积极面对苦难与挑战，不断突破自我，最终将命运始终牢牢地把握在自己手中！</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1066/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="仙逆">仙逆</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至147集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1239/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="凡人修仙传" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.jisuimage.com/cover/199232257dffb88971fd8755abf20863.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="凡人修仙传"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2020</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-ru"><span class="rebo">热播</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1239/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="凡人修仙传">凡人修仙传</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%92%B1%E6%96%87%E9%9D%92.html" target="_blank">钱文青</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%A8%E5%A4%A9%E7%BF%94.html" target="_blank">杨天翔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%A8%E9%BB%98.html" target="_blank">杨默</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%AD%AA%E6%AD%AA.html" target="_blank">歪歪</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B0%B7%E6%B1%9F%E5%B1%B1.html" target="_blank">谷江山</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B9%94%E8%AF%97%E8%AF%AD.html" target="_blank">乔诗语</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BD%9F%E5%BF%83%E7%AB%B9.html" target="_blank">佟心竹</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　平凡少年韩立出生贫困，为了让家人过上更好的生活，自愿前去七玄门参加入门考核，最终被墨大夫收入门下。　　墨大夫一开始对韩立悉心培养、传授医术，让韩立对他非常感激，但随着一同入门的弟子张铁失踪，韩立才</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/1239/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="凡人修仙传">凡人修仙传</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第180集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/137195/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="九阳武神" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.jisuimage.com/cover/95d952510e02ffba7fa228e4d43866cb.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="九阳武神"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-ru"><span class="vip">独家推荐</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/137195/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="九阳武神">九阳武神</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%A9%AC%E6%AD%A3%E9%98%B3.html" target="_blank">马正阳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B9%BD%E8%88%9E%E8%B6%8A%E5%B1%B1.html" target="_blank">幽舞越山</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　前世叶云飞天资过人，但体内武脉突然关闭，无法练武，遭遇了家族内部的奚落，未婚妻的私通背叛，各家族的围剿，让少年叶云飞众叛亲离，好友被欺凌、挚爱伤心离开、父亲惨烈战死。好在云游路过的紫圣真君将他收入</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/137195/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="九阳武神">九阳武神</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至第34集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/169856/sid/1/nid/1.html" tit