iv class="module-list module-lines-list"><div class="module-items"><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="京武侠影" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260301-1/911f8f15d83fae78505081d36efc75f3.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="京武侠影"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2021</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="京武侠影">京武侠影</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B4%9B%E6%99%A8%E8%88%92.html" target="_blank">洛晨舒</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">少林寺开光大典在即，在开光大典之日向外界展览镇寺之宝灵龟胆。这一消息不仅让中国的武林人士蠢蠢欲动，就连外国的几大高手也来到了中国，打算窃取灵龟胆。少林俗家弟子袁世勇为保护灵龟胆与敌人展开了殊死搏斗</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="京武侠影">京武侠影</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD国语</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="亚洲的独特国度" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-29/202606291782741547.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="亚洲的独特国度"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="亚洲的独特国度">亚洲的独特国度</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%84%AD%E4%BA%9C%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">鄭亜美</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B2%A9%E6%9C%AC%E3%81%88%E3%82%8A.html" target="_blank">岩本えり</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%87%91%E5%AD%90%E5%B2%B3%E6%86%B2.html" target="_blank">金子岳憲</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B2%A9%E8%B0%B7%E5%81%A5%E5%8F%B8.html" target="_blank">岩谷健司</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　本作是以东京都内某栋独户住宅为舞台的&amp;quot;纯粹社会派深刻喜剧&amp;quot;。曜子在丈夫工作期间，既在一楼照料公公，又在二楼经营非法风俗店。对政治与社会保持敏感、同时竭力兼顾看护工作与风俗营业的</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="亚洲的独特国度">亚洲的独特国度</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="自足者富" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/b564bc1ba1a23f080480c22ffe6da1a4.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="自足者富"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>印度</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="自足者富">自足者富</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%A1%9E%E7%BC%AA%E6%8B%89%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%BC.html" target="_blank">塞缪拉卡尼</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Gautham+Vasudev+Menon.html" target="_blank">Gautham Vasudev Menon</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Abhinaya.html" target="_blank">Abhinaya</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">சமுத்திரக்கனி, கவுதம் வாசுதேவ் மேனன் முதன்மை வேடங்களில் நடித்துள்ள திரைப்படம் ‘கார்மேனி செல்வம்’. லட</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="自足者富">自足者富</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="牛骷髅村" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260623-1/2e0874521ae4fa3d1f6a7e4073fadbb1.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="牛骷髅村"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>泰国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="牛骷髅村">牛骷髅村</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9C%C2%B7%E9%A2%82%E6%A1%91.html" target="_blank">巴东·颂桑</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Kapol+Thongplub+.html" target="_blank"> Kapol Thongplub </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BA%B3%E6%9F%A5%C2%B7%E4%BD%B3%E5%A1%94%E6%BD%98.html" target="_blank">纳查·佳塔潘</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Yotsawat+Tawapee+.html" target="_blank"> Yotsawat Tawapee </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Kanchai+Kumnoetploy+.html" target="_blank"> Kanchai Kumnoetploy </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BF%81%E5%8A%A0%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E5%A5%91%E5%A7%86%E6%9F%A5%E9%B2%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%BA%93%E5%B0%94.html" target="_blank">翁加特·契姆查鲁本库尔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%90%A8%E5%93%88%E6%9F%A5%C2%B7%E6%A5%9A%E5%A7%86%E9%B2%81%E5%A7%86.html" target="_blank">萨哈查·楚姆鲁姆</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B2%99%E5%8D%A1%C2%B7%E6%9F%B4%E6%9D%BE.html" target="_blank">亚沙卡·柴松</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Aukkarat+Jittasiri.html" target="_blank"> Aukkarat Jittasiri</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">偏远闭塞的科卡洛克村突发连环诡杀，所有男性死者均下体溃烂、死状狰狞，现场只留诡异巫术印记。全村陷入恐慌，人人都说是百年前被虐杀沉塘的怨灵冲破封印，回村血债血偿。专案组深入荒村查案，一边撞见层出不穷的灵异异象，一边挖出村落世代掩埋的黑暗原罪。死亡人数持续飙升，线索反复反转，所有人都困在人鬼难辨的死局里：到底是复仇怨灵血洗全村，还是有人借鬼之名，把整座村落变成了自己的屠宰场？</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="牛骷髅村">牛骷髅村</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD中字</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180647/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="鬼区死守" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260623-1/c57b87c1da89ba90cba79c75e7bb6756.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="鬼区死守"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180647/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="鬼区死守">鬼区死守</a></div><div