item-style video-text">　　《超级红人榜》是三立电视的歌唱选秀节目，由于美人与蔡昌宪、许志豪 联合主持，怡佳娱乐制作，制作人为张玉川、谢孟芬，2010年11月7日开播。三立台湾台每周日18：30~20：00播出，当日22：0</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/950/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="超级红人榜">超级红人榜</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260628</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饥饿游戏" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.ffzy888.com/upload/vod/20221107-1/6107492c0ec31992e852b4747899364c.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="饥饿游戏"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2016</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>台湾</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饥饿游戏">饥饿游戏</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AD%99%E5%8D%8F%E5%BF%97.html" target="_blank">孙协志</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8E%8B%E4%BB%81%E7%94%AB.html" target="_blank">王仁甫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%AE%B8%E5%AD%9F%E5%93%B2.html" target="_blank">许孟哲</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　史上最餓劣的食境節目【飢餓遊戲】點選以下連結訂閱，精采影音不漏接！　　史上最&amp;amp;quot;靠夭&amp;amp;quot;的節目　　今天的戰友．明天的敵人　　永遠無法預知下一關將跟與誰合作　　唯有帶著【玩下去、吃下</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="饥饿游戏">饥饿游戏</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260628</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/322/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="11点热吵店" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloade