ri</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Minase.html" target="_blank">Minase</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%9F%B3%E8%B0%B7%E6%98%A5%E8%B4%B5.html" target="_blank">石谷春贵</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%80%AC%E6%88%B8%E8%8A%AD%E6%9C%88.html" target="_blank">瀬戸芭月</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　以室町时代为舞台，讲述了后来被称为世阿弥的美少年“鬼夜叉”的故事。在一切以技艺为重的父亲观阿弥身边长大，鬼夜叉始终无法理解人类为何会享受艺术与表演。某一天，他在村子边缘的一户民宅中，看见一名唱歌跳</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181270/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="世界在起舞">世界在起舞</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至01集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/170746/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="冰之城墙" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-04-02/202604021775145267.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="冰之城墙"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/170746/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="冰之城墙">冰之城墙</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B0%B8%E6%BF%91%E5%AE%89%E5%A5%88.html" target="_blank">永濑安奈</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%92%8C%E6%B3%89%E9%A3%8E%E8%8A%B1.html" target="_blank">和泉风花</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%8D%83%E5%8F%B6%E7%BF%94%E4%B9%9F.html" target="_blank">千叶翔也</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8C%AA%E8%82%A1%E6%85%A7%E5%A3%AB.html" target="_blank">猪股慧士</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%96%B0%E7%A6%8F%E6%A8%B1.html" target="_blank">新福樱</a>&nbsp;<a href="/ind