"/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%8D%89%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E5%BC%A5.html" target="_blank">草川拓弥</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%A3%E7%BA%B1%E5%BC%A5%E5%8A%A0.html" target="_blank">山口纱弥加</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%8A%E5%B7%9D%E6%8B%93%E9%83%8E.html" target="_blank">上川拓郎</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B0%8F%E6%9D%BE%E5%92%8C%E9%87%8D.html" target="_blank">小松和重</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">日本每年有约20万具遗体被归为“死因不明”，真正接受法医学解剖的不足一成。为改变这一现状，厚生劳动省主导成立了拥有调查指示与解剖决定权的法医学专业团队——MEJ（Medical Examiner Ja</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/171775/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="所爱之人">所爱之人</a></div><div class="module-item-text">全11集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/171059/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="摩绪" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-04-05/202604051775349945.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="摩绪"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">动漫</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/171059/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="摩绪">摩绪</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%A2%B6%E8%A3%95%E8%B4%B5.html" target="_blank">梶裕贵</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%9D%E4%BA%95%E7%94%B0%E5%A4%8F%E6%B5%B7.html" target="_blank">川井田夏海</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AF%BA%E6%B3%BD%E7%99%BE%E8%8A%B1.html" target="_blank">寺泽百花</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%8B%E9%87%8E%E7%BA%AE.html" target="_blank">下野纮</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%B0%E6%B0%B8%E5%88%A9%E8%A1%8C.html" target="_blank">丰永利行</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%85%B4%E6%B4%A5%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B8.html" target="_blank">兴津和幸</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E3%81%8F%E3%81%BE%E3%81%84%E3%82%82%E3%81%A8%E3%81%93.html" target="_blank">くまいもとこ</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%97%A5%E7%AC%A0%E9%98%B3%E5%AD%90.html" target="_blank">日笠阳子</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E7%90%86%E6%B2%99.html" target="_blank">清水理沙</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%B8%8A%E7%94%B0%E4%B8%BD%E5%A5%88.html" target="_blank">上田丽奈</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%BE%E5%B1%B1%E9%B9%B0%E5%BF%97.html" target="_blank">松山鹰志</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　生活在现代的青年——摩绪（MAO）。因&amp;quot;诅咒&amp;quot;而存活了 900 年的神秘阴阳师。生活在令和时代的女中学生黄叶菜花。幼年时遭遇事故，全家只有她一人幸存。某日，当菜花穿过那扇已成为</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/171059/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="摩绪">摩绪</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至13集</div></div></div></div><div class="module-footer"><a href="/index.php/vod/show/id/1.html" class="load-all" title="更多">查看更多<i class="icon-arrow-right-o"></i></a></div></div><div class="module-list module-line-list tab-list"><div class="module-items scroll-box"><div class="scroll-content"><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="京武侠影" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260301-1/911f8f15d83fae78505081d36efc75f3.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="京武侠影"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2021</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="京武侠影">京武侠影</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B4%9B%E6%99%A8%E8%88%92.html" target="_blank">洛晨舒</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">少林寺开光大典在即，在开光大典之日向外界展览镇寺之宝灵龟胆。这一消息不仅让中国的武林人士蠢蠢欲动，就连外国的几大高手也来到了中国，打算窃取灵龟胆。少林俗家弟子袁世勇为保护灵龟胆与敌人展开了殊死搏斗</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/166438/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="京武侠影">京武侠影</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD国语</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="亚洲的独特国度" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-29/202606291782741547.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="亚洲的独特国度"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="亚洲的独特国度">亚洲的独特国度</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%84%AD%E4%BA%9C%E7%BE%8E.html" target="_blank">鄭亜美</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B2%A9%E6%9C%AC%E3%81%88%E3%82%8A.html" target="_blank">岩本えり</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%87%91%E5%AD%90%E5%B2%B3%E6%86%B2.html" target="_blank">金子岳憲</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B2%A9%E8%B0%B7%E5%81%A5%E5%8F%B8.html" target="_blank">岩谷健司</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　本作是以东京都内某栋独户住宅为舞台的&amp;quot;纯粹社会派深刻喜剧&amp;quot;。曜子在丈夫工作期间，既在一楼照料公公，又在二楼经营非法风俗店。对政治与社会保持敏感、同时竭力兼顾看护工作与风俗营业的</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181271/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="亚洲的独特国度">亚洲的独特国度</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="自足者富" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/b564bc1ba1a23f080480c22ffe6da1a4.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="自足者富"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>印度</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="自足者富">自足者富</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%A1%9E%E7%BC%AA%E6%8B%89%E5%8D%A1%E5%B0%BC.html" target="_blank">塞缪拉卡尼</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Gautham+Vasudev+Menon.html" target="_blank">Gautham Vasudev Menon</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Abhinaya.html" target="_blank">Abhinaya</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">சமுத்திரக்கனி, கவுதம் வாசுதேவ் மேனன் முதன்மை வேடங்களில் நடித்துள்ள திரைப்படம் ‘கார்மேனி செல்வம்’. லட</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181249/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="自足者富">自足者富</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="牛骷髅村" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260623-1/2e0874521ae4fa3d1f6a7e4073fadbb1.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="牛骷髅村"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>泰国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="牛骷髅村">牛骷髅村</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%B7%B4%E4%B8%9C%C2%B7%E9%A2%82%E6%A1%91.html" target="_blank">巴东·颂桑</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Kapol+Thongplub+.html" target="_blank"> Kapol Thongplub </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BA%B3%E6%9F%A5%C2%B7%E4%BD%B3%E5%A1%94%E6%BD%98.html" target="_blank">纳查·佳塔潘</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Yotsawat+Tawapee+.html" target="_blank"> Yotsawat Tawapee </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Kanchai+Kumnoetploy+.html" target="_blank"> Kanchai Kumnoetploy </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%BF%81%E5%8A%A0%E7%89%B9%C2%B7%E5%A5%91%E5%A7%86%E6%9F%A5%E9%B2%81%E6%9C%AC%E5%BA%93%E5%B0%94.html" target="_blank">翁加特·契姆查鲁本库尔</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%90%A8%E5%93%88%E6%9F%A5%C2%B7%E6%A5%9A%E5%A7%86%E9%B2%81%E5%A7%86.html" target="_blank">萨哈查·楚姆鲁姆</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BA%9A%E6%B2%99%E5%8D%A1%C2%B7%E6%9F%B4%E6%9D%BE.html" target="_blank">亚沙卡·柴松</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Aukkarat+Jittasiri.html" target="_blank"> Aukkarat Jittasiri</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">偏远闭塞的科卡洛克村突发连环诡杀，所有男性死者均下体溃烂、死状狰狞，现场只留诡异巫术印记。全村陷入恐慌，人人都说是百年前被虐杀沉塘的怨灵冲破封印，回村血债血偿。专案组深入荒村查案，一边撞见层出不穷的灵异异象，一边挖出村落世代掩埋的黑暗原罪。死亡人数持续飙升，线索反复反转，所有人都困在人鬼难辨的死局里：到底是复仇怨灵血洗全村，还是有人借鬼之名，把整座村落变成了自己的屠宰场？</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180597/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="牛骷髅村">牛骷髅村</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD中字</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180647/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="鬼区死守" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260623-1/c57b87c1da89ba90cba79c75e7bb6756.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="鬼区死守"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180647/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="鬼区死守">鬼区死守</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%A9%AC%E5%85%8B%C2%B7%E9%98%BF%E4%BB%80%E6%B2%83%E6%96%AF.html" target="_blank">马克·阿什沃斯</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+George+Quinones+.html" target="_blank"> George Quinones </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Chris+Mayers.html" target="_blank"> Chris Mayers</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">After moving to the suburbs, a young couple finds themselves trapped in an epic battle between their new HOA and an onslaught of monsters from hell.</div></div>