6</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181110/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="午夜电梯">午夜电梯</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%88%98%E5%8D%9A.html" target="_blank">刘博</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B5%B5%E5%B8%85.html" target="_blank">赵帅</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　午夜子时，血色符纸在电梯口燃尽，连接阴阳的“鬼奠梯”就此开启。 因为老宅拆迁，落魄女作家李心凌被迫回到重庆。然而，她惊恐地发现，每到午夜12点，那部废弃的电梯都会自行启动。电梯每开一次门，就有一位</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181110/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="午夜电梯">午夜电梯</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181008/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="幻犬诳猫" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-27/202606271782533776.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="幻犬诳猫"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">电影</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181008/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="幻犬诳猫">幻犬诳猫</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%AB%98%E6%9D%89%E7%9C%9F%E5%AE%99.html" target="_blank">高杉真宙</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BC%8A%E8%97%A4%E4%B8%87%E7%90%86%E5%8D%8E.html" target="_blank">伊藤万理华</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B7%B1%E5%B7%9D%E9%BA%BB%E8%A1%A3.html" target="_blank">深川麻衣</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AE%89%E8%97%A4%E8%A3%95%E5%AD%90.html" target="_