odule-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/950/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="超级红人榜" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.ffzy888.com/upload/vod/20221107-1/f763daed7265c9154d77c64ed72ae514.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="超级红人榜"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2010</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>台湾</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/950/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="超级红人榜">超级红人榜</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BA%8E%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%BA.html" target="_blank">于美人</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%94%A1%E6%98%8C%E5%AE%AA.html" target="_blank">蔡昌宪</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%AE%B8%E5%BF%97%E8%B1%AA.html" target="_blank">许志豪</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B1%9F%E6%83%A0%E4%BB%AA.html" target="_blank">江惠仪</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　《超级红人榜》是三立电视的歌唱选秀节目，由于美人与蔡昌宪、许志豪 联合主持，怡佳娱乐制作，制作人为张玉川、谢孟芬，2010年11月7日开播。三立台湾台每周日18：30~20：00播出，当日22：0</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/950/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="超级红人榜">超级红人榜</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260628</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饥饿游戏" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.ffzy888.com/upload/vod/20221107-1/6107492c0ec31992e852b4747899364c.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="饥饿游戏"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2016</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>台湾</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饥饿游戏">饥饿游戏</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AD%99%E5%8D%8F%E5%BF%97.html" target="_blank">孙协志</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8E%8B%E4%BB%81%E7%94%AB.html" target="_blank">王仁甫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%AE%B8%E5%AD%9F%E5%93%B2.html" target="_blank">许孟哲</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　史上最餓劣的食境節目【飢餓遊戲】點選以下連結訂閱，精采影音不漏接！　　史上最&amp;amp;quot;靠夭&amp;amp;quot;的節目　　今天的戰友．明天的敵人　　永遠無法預知下一關將跟與誰合作　　唯有帶著【玩下去、吃下</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/949/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="饥饿游戏">饥饿游戏</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260628</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/322/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="11点热吵店" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.ffzy888.com/upload/vod/20221102-1/8955744064482505eff4a4659c4ed885.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="11点热吵店"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2020</span><span class="video-class">综艺</span><span>台湾</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/322/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="11点热吵店">11点热吵店</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%B2%88%E7%8E%89%E7%90%B3.html" target="_blank">沈玉琳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%AE%B7%E6%82%A6.html" target="_blank">殷悦</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　TVBS欢乐台42频道推出全新节目《11点热吵店》，荒谬大师沈玉琳遇上疯疯贵妇Melody竟是“地