tatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="北京小妞"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>1991</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181261/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="北京小妞">北京小妞</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%AB%98%E6%94%BE.html" target="_blank">高放</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E4%BE%AF%E8%80%80%E5%8D%8E.html" target="_blank">侯耀华</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%87%8C%E5%85%83.html" target="_blank">凌元</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%A9%AC%E9%9B%85%E8%88%92.html" target="_blank">马雅舒</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%AD%99%E4%BD%B3%E6%98%9F.html" target="_blank">孙佳星</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E6%A5%A0.html" target="_blank">李楠</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%96%B9%E5%AD%90%E5%93%A5.html" target="_blank">方子哥</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B5%B5%E5%AD%90%E5%B2%B3.html" target="_blank">赵子岳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E7%8E%8B%E6%BE%8D.html" target="_blank">王澍</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%A4%8F%E5%AE%97%E5%AD%A6.html" target="_blank">夏宗学</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%99%88%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%AD.html" target="_blank">陈立中</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9D%8E%E5%94%90.html" target="_blank">李唐</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%9B.html" target="_blank">劳力</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%83%91%E4%BF%9D%E6%B0%91.html" target="_blank">郑保民</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%A2%81%E7%8E%AB.html" target="_blank">袁玫</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">&amp;nbsp;文静清秀的女孩金京（马雅舒饰）是北京“花裙子艺术团”的会计，她总是默默地为大家服务，腼腆又胆小。一日回家路上，刚刚得到的捐款被流氓抢劫一空，并且在流氓的威胁下，金京没敢揭穿他们。此事让她后</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181261/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="北京小妞">北京小妞</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD中字</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180991/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="731实录日本731部队新罪证披露" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.lzipic.com/upload/vod/20260627-1/c1ce25eba7b4cd8032d7f27024569ca8.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="731实录日本731部队新罪证披露"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span></span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180991/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="731实录日本731部队新罪证披露">731实录日本731部队新罪证披露</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">暂无内容</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180991/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="731实录日本731部队新罪证披露">731实录日本731部队新罪证披露</a></div><div class="module-item-text">已完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/176586/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="人生不过几顿饭" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260514-1/c1dc4f6e9010e8b509b50afef62d6fce.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="人生不过几顿饭"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/176586/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="人生不过几顿饭">人生不过几顿饭</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">纪录片《人生不过几顿饭》是一场横跨中国大地对于当下人生大事的深度观察。镜头穿过婚宴的喧闹、满月酒的期盼、升学宴的焦灼、散伙饭的释然、乔迁宴的向往、庆功宴的激昂与生命谢宴的沉静，记录当下一个个普通人如何在饭桌之上，“签收”自己的人生。这里没有预设的完美剧本，只有真实的欢笑、泪水、争执与拥抱。它让我们看到，每一张看似普通的餐桌上，都上演着关于爱情、亲情、勇气、和解、传承与重生的生命大戏。人生不过几顿饭，但正是这几顿饭的温度，让我们在往后的柴米油盐中，有了反复燃起的希望。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/176586/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="人生不过几顿饭">人生不过几顿饭</a></div><div class="module-item-text">全7集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180710/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="西汉皇后传" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/0db0c4bf1bd7f11839c8add95e5bb03c.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="西汉皇后传"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180710/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="西汉皇后传">西汉皇后传</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">《西汉皇后传》以西汉王朝兴衰为时间线，聚焦先后登上后位的一众女子，串联起近百年的后宫朝堂风云。她们身份迥异，际遇天差地别：有人凭才情与恩宠从底层逆袭，执掌凤印；有人身负家族期许入宫，沦为朝堂制衡的棋子</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180710/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="西汉皇后传">西汉皇后传</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第10集已完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178272/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="盛唐前夜" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/8b3b4862662f2fe55cdf756a9e394804.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="盛唐前夜"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178272/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="盛唐前夜">盛唐前夜</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">隋，三百年乱世孕育而生的强大帝国，多民族融合后的大一统王朝。可仅仅三十八年，这个富裕而强大的帝国便轰然崩塌。在隋末乱世的棋局中，“战神”李世民横扫各路反王，平定四方。然后用一场精心布置的棋局(玄武门之</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178272/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="盛唐前夜">盛唐前夜</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第10集已完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181232/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="尘嚣低语" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/87b7871b0e1c7de0145d3f5076f172b9.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="尘嚣低语"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181232/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="尘嚣低语">尘嚣低语</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Norma+Adams-Wade+.html" target="_blank">Norma Adams-Wade </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+George+Elbert+Adams+.html" target="_blank"> George Elbert Adams </a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/+Stella+Mae+Byrd.html" target="_blank"> Stella Mae Byrd</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">African American volunteers in Jasper, Texas work to overcome their community&amp;#039;s history of racial violence and reclaim dignity through grassroots projects, museums, and memorials following the 1998 lynching of James Byrd Jr.</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181232/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="尘嚣低语">尘嚣低语</a></div><div class="module-item-text">已完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/33973/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="跟着书本去旅行" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2023-10-14/202310141697275590.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="跟着书本去旅行"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2019</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/33973/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="跟着书本去旅行">跟着书本去旅行</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%86%85%E8%AF%A6.html" target="_blank">内详</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　《跟着书本去旅行》是一档体验式文化教育节目。节目以中小学课本或经典名著为线索，在读万卷书的同时行万里路，走近文化古迹、实地实景讲故事、身临其境受教育，触摸历史、感知文化，让陈列在广阔大地上的遗产活</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/33973/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="跟着书本去旅行">跟着书本去旅行</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260629</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181194/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="舍得智慧人物第八季" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/e4c114d6b5c09739ec3f7c9e69a85a15.png" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="舍得智慧人物第八季"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181194/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="舍得智慧人物第八季">舍得智慧人物第八季</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">时间的长河里，什么是人生最笃定的答案？本季节目给出它的注解：因为热爱，所以舍得。真正的热爱，不是一时的激情，而是无论历经多少起伏与拉扯，依然指引前行的心灯。当一个人找到了心之所向，人生中所有的“舍”便不再是艰难彷徨的算计，而是水到渠成的从容。我们不谈宏大叙事，只聊真实人生。本季节目将讨论范围延伸至教育、爱情、职业、代际、个人成长等具体社会议题。邀请文化、艺术、心理、商业、体育等领域的时代人物，分享他们在人生转折处的关键抉择。在这里，没有生硬的说教，只有同频共振的交心。愿你在这些鲜活的生命样本中，找到稳住人</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181194/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="舍得智慧人物第八季">舍得智慧人物第八季</a></div><div class="module-item-text">更新至20260629</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181186/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-29/202606291782662900.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181186/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客">饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年，一直都在逃离【食贫道视频播客】</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181186/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客">饼叔首次自述丨我的前40年一直都在逃离食贫道视频播客</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD国语</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181150/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="萨昆" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-28/202606281782646578.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="萨昆"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181150/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="萨昆">萨昆</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%90%A8%E6%98%86%C2%B7%E5%B7%B4%E5%85%8B%E5%88%A9.html" target="_blank">萨昆·巴克利</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　萨昆·巴克利 (Saquon Barkley) 随费城老鹰队夺得超级碗冠军的历程，展现了他作为一名精英 NFL 跑卫在伤病和合同纠纷中展现出的韧性，以及他作为一名忠诚的父亲、丈夫和朋友的坚定性格。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181150/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="萨昆">萨昆</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD中字</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181148/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-06-28/202606281782646459.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>加拿大</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181148/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争">大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　Reflecting on the history of Toronto’s queer community, one of Parade’s participants notes, “Toron</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181148/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争">大游行多伦多酷儿的爱与抗争</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD中字</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180941/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260626-1/be74fc13f19e2027afc05c3da4c6aa9e.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180941/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘">克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">暂无剧情介绍</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180941/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘">克里斯与玛蒂娜最后一盘</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178921/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="信仰奴隶福音使者" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://www.imgzy360.com:7788/upload/vod/20260606-1/925c97829da7d8dda552ad3589b69eca.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="信仰奴隶福音使者"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>巴西</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178921/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="信仰奴隶福音使者">信仰奴隶福音使者</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/Jo%C3%A3o+Cl%C3%A1+Dias.html" target="_blank">João Clá Dias</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">&amp;quot;Escravos da Fé: Os Arautos do Evangelho&amp;quot; é o título de um documentário investigativo da H</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/178921/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="信仰奴隶福音使者">信仰奴隶福音使者</a></div><div class="module-item-text">完结</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181077/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/2f8233a7889034a01a9e66bd9d2cefde.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181077/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史">生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%8B%89%E9%87%8C%C2%B7%E5%A4%A7%E5%8D%AB.html" target="_blank">拉里·大卫</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%AF%94%E5%B0%94%C2%B7%E5%93%88%E5%BE%B7%E5%B0%94.html" target="_blank">比尔·哈德尔</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">作为美国建国250周年的献礼，该剧以拉里·大卫标志性的冷幽默与全即兴风格，通过情景喜剧形式荒诞地重新演绎美国历史上的各个标志性时刻。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181077/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史">生活拉里与不快乐的追求一部美国史</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第1集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180313/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="地球劫后重生" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/8f49acedecba49bd3240e886f923abd3.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="地球劫后重生"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180313/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="地球劫后重生">地球劫后重生</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">从2026年6月11日起，每周四晚，让我们齐聚一堂，共同领略自然世界的奇观。NBC将通过《幸存地球》带观众领略4.5亿年的生命史。这部里程碑式的系列剧颂扬了生命惊人的韧性以及每一种生物为延续至今所经历</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/180313/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="地球劫后重生">地球劫后重生</a></div><div class="module-item-text">第3集</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181058/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.lzipic.com/upload/vod/20260627-1/d74a3b93f7409fe40a24a1074855be81.webp" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">纪录片</span><span>美国</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181058/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生">AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">源于强烈焦虑的艺术作品，总有一种深层的吸引力——或许是因为它源自脆弱，也源自对清晰的渴求。《AI启示录：一个末日乐观主义者的诞生》正源于联合导演丹尼尔·罗尔对未来的深切不安，尤其是人工智能在塑造未来中</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181058/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生">AI启示录一个末日乐观主义者的诞生</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD</div></div></div></div><div class="module-footer"><a href="/index.php/vod/type/id/6.html" class="load-all" title="查看更多纪录片">更多纪录片<i class="icon-arrow-right-o"></i></a></div></div><div class="module-list module-line-list tab-list"><div class="module-items scroll-box"><div class="scroll-content"><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181229/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="锦鲤人间之如愿以偿" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://img.picbf.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/85a2dd11d00870257d6a847077560b6f.png" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="锦鲤人间之如愿以偿"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">少儿</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181229/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="锦鲤人间之如愿以偿">锦鲤人间之如愿以偿</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">弟弟李鲸被暗玉浊气侵蚀危在旦夕，父亲李鲲离奇失踪，走投无路的少年李鲥，在家传鲲佩的指引下，召唤出来自鲲域的锦鲤仙李鲤。为报李家先祖的救命之恩，傲娇灵动的锦鲤仙与执着坚定的人间少年，结伴踏上了一场险象环生的大冒险。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181229/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="锦鲤人间之如愿以偿">锦鲤人间之如愿以偿</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD国语</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181248/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="黄色之星" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://hongniuzyimage.com/cover/213aac604c535d3193d0e77427bfa34f.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="黄色之星"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>1996</span><span class="video-class">少儿</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181248/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="黄色之星">黄色之星</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E6%9C%AA%E7%9F%A5.html" target="_blank">未知</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">故事围绕一名年轻的少女展开。剧情讲述女主角的母亲给她找了一位继父，而这位看似体面的继父实际上与贩毒的街头混混暗中勾结。在继女备考期间，继父对其伸出了魔爪，将无辜的女主角卷入了一场充满阴谋与暴力的危机之</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181248/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="黄色之星">黄色之星</a></div><div class="module-item-text">正片</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181201/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="精灵王国重返小人国" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic.youkupic.com/upload/vod/20260629-1/3910cf772103bb41dfa2f7d6621fc726.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="精灵王国重返小人国"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2025</span><span class="video-class">少儿</span><span>大陆</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181201/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="精灵王国重返小人国">精灵王国重返小人国</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E9%83%AD%E6%96%87%E6%B3%BD.html" target="_blank">郭文泽</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%B5%B5%E5%A8%85%E5%A9%B7.html" target="_blank">赵娅婷</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%88%98%E9%9B%AA%E8%89%B3.html" target="_blank">刘雪艳</a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search.html" target="_blank"></a>&nbsp;<a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E8%83%A1%E5%90%AB%E6%9C%88.html" target="_blank">胡含月</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">神奇的文字记录着世界上发生过的每一件事情，但随着时间的流逝，这些文字会褪色，模糊，人类的记忆也会随之消失。 有这样一群小精灵，他们生活在另一个奇异世界，精灵们勤劳善良，他们用魔法对抗着时间。</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/181201/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="精灵王国重返小人国">精灵王国重返小人国</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD国语</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/174711/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https://pic3.yzzyimg.online/upload/vod/2026-05-04/202605041777861422.jpg" src="/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/loading.gif" onerror="javascript:this.src='/template/mxone/mxstatic/image/zanwupic.png'" alt="关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇"><div class="loading"></div></div><div class="module-item-caption"><span>2026</span><span class="video-class">少儿</span><span>日本</span></div><div class="module-item-content"><div class="module-item-style video-name"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/174711/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇">关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇</a></div><div class="module-item-style video-tag"><a href="/index.php/vod/search/actor/%E5%A0%82%E6%9C%AC%E5%85%89%E4%B8%80.html" target="_blank">堂本光一</a>&nbsp;</div><div class="module-item-style video-text">　　舞台设定在崇拜水龙守护神的海底王国「海炎国」，这里因神秘污染和“强行唤醒沉睡水龙”的阴谋陷入危机。利姆露一行人原本是来海岛度假，却被卷入这场深海危机，从悠闲摸鱼被迫营业，潜入苍海深处揭开阴谋、阻止</div></div></div><div class="module-item-titlebox"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/174711/sid/1/nid/1.html" class="module-item-title" title="关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇">关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇</a></div><div class="module-item-text">HD</div></div><div class="module-item"><div class="module-item-cover"><div class="module-item-pic"><a href="/index.php/vod/play/id/174682/sid/1/nid/1.html" title="关于我转生变成史莱姆这档事苍海之泪篇劇場版" ><i class="icon-play"></i></a><img class="lazy lazyloaded" data-src="https: